CLEAN COMMAND
what if we have not that file on stage,
in other word restore an untracked file!
in this situation because the restore command can not find the file
it get some error.
clean command will remove all untracked files.

git clean
fatal: clean.requireForce is true and -f not    given: refusing to clean

Note: git say, hey it's a dangerous
      if you delete untracked files, you can not restore them!
      so you should use -f to force him clean the files!
      use help to see all options on clean
      (git clean -h)


git clean -fd    //force the command to delete all the untracked files
                 //"d" will remove all untracked directory too!